But it also has drawbacks. many center filters require a factor of 1.5 or 2 in the aperture filter, which may increase the necessary closure time in such a way that it is impossible to hold the camera with the hand. wide angle lenses should also use a center filter, an aperture of f / 16 or less, otherwise blurred effects caused by movement.
