The toolbar contains seven buttons to navigate with which you can jump to the current / first / last difference, to the next / previous difference (Ctrl-down / Ctrl-Up), to the next / previous conflict (Ctrl-Out / Ctrl-Out) or to the next / previous unresolved conflict. therefore, conflicts between resolved and unresolved conflicts must be distinguished.
To copy the clipboard mark you have to copy the Copy button (Ctrl-C or Ctrl-Insert). if this option is checked, whatever you select is automatically copied to the clipboard and the manual copying is omitted.
